      "Our position is the opposite, and it's the core reason to choose us. **You own the equipment outright. Oil is month-to-month with no minimum term.** No three-month lock-in, no auto-shipped oil you didn't ask for, no lease you have to buy your way out of when you renovate or close a location. If a competitor's headline price requires a subscription to unlock, price the full term, not the sticker — that's the real number. Our [pillar comparison](/blog/best-commercial-scent-diffuser) lines the major commercial brands up on exactly these terms.",
