      "### Why does my coffee shop smell stale or sour even though we clean?",
      "The usual culprits sit outside the bar where the coffee aroma can't reach — floor drains and the dish area, the milk fridge and steam wand, trash that's sat through the rush, and a closed-up room with poor airflow by late afternoon. Address those sources and improve ventilation first; scent is only a finishing layer on top of a clean space.",
