      "A waiting room that smells clean and welcoming is one of the simplest upgrades a clinic, office, or salon can make — and the order matters: fresh air, clean furnishings, and a fresh restroom first, then a light, responsible scent as the finishing layer. For a single waiting area, the [Atmos Wi-Fi standalone unit](/product/autivora-atmos-wifi-diffuser) is the place to start; for multiple locations or wholesale pricing, [get in touch](/contact).",
